    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，起源下面放两个子节点：一个是「悠久历史」，我想给它加个书本图标；另一个是「普及化」，这个要再细一层，指向Tony Buzan——那位英国大众心理学作家。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Long history",
        "Popularisation",
        "British popular psychology author Tony Buzan",
        "icon(fa fa-book)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
